static struct nidrange* add_nidrange ( const struct cfs_lstr *  src,
struct list_head *  nidlist 
) [static, read]

Finds or creates struct nidrange.

Checks if src is a valid network name, looks for corresponding nidrange on the ist of nidranges (nidlist), creates new struct nidrange if it is not found.

Return values:
pointer to struct nidrange matching network specified via src
NULL if src does not match any network

int cfs_parse_nidlist ( char *  str,
int  len,
struct list_head *  nidlist 
)

Parses nid range list.

Parses with rigorous syntax and overflow checking str into <nidrange> [ ' ' <nidrange> ], compiles str into set of structures and links that structure to nidlist. The resulting list can be used to match a NID againts set of NIDS defined by str.

See also:
cfs_match_nid
Return values:
1 on success
0 otherwise
